{"tid":1953880,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"希望做唔住嘅黃店推出飯券\"預先付款\"","createTime":"2020-04-01T12:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T04:31:58.000Z","uid":101117,"like":56,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5aa4181c181fc60b33a9fb5c5227aef7ce0942","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"黃店每日畀人搞鳩<br />\n淋紅油嘅有、畀狗揸住把尺屈唔夠1.5米又有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪應該推出飯券畀大家預先付款<br />\n幫手解決cash flow 嘅燃眉之急 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段時間真係唔係唔想幫襯<br />\n但係真係寧願唔出街 <br />\n雖然可以嗌Foodpanda <br />\n但入我地址 reach 唔到自己區入面嘅黃店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考如下: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TskR4A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TskR4A.png&h=a0822698&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLink: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kimchifriedinews/photos/a.551126505417357/761039027759436/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkimchifriedinews%2Fphotos%2Fa.551126505417357%2F761039027759436%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=830f871b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kimchifriedinews/photos/a.551126505417357/761039027759436/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n咁樣或者可以吸納更多店加入黃色陣營 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係想人血饅頭<br />\n但抗爭都要喺日常生活入面維持<br />\n尤其依家好難出街，行過都要被老屈多過4個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04bbd29d2e8b5738f905dd9d7e86d78ef09da9b","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7d7e122a8e5c938d14ec064339fe86f68490ab15","tid":1953880,"uid":1159,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"到時執咗就變軍票"},{"pid":"91ecdae2299b76bf5c21cde29a8b973b59afb846","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f5724d61d59b826f1360398cfdd086e8a11cc9ac","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"be6e06a59b6c2ee23a379cb43a996eb17c3f3348","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"112c9ff840e12846b748c88c189374176f11730c","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3bd6dfac4f55240b21f24dd38c24529a7f127114","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6abf355e98bae0f8ac6b861fc9ea429741e9932d","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"914c163f7fc56fdd4f38ab190c91eaf34fc63911","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"cf58243720b87a4615a9da14189523982181af4e","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"a80119027a7316b3705f3319aacad42ea2694b68","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:26:17.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"4b399f5583ebaec83ecd93a854b1e965504a58b2","tid":1953880,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-